Prove (3.30)
by showing the LHS is equivalent to the RHS

Proof:
  p ⋁ false
=    〈 (3.15) ¬p ≡ p ≡ false 〉
  p ⋁ (¬p ≡ p)
=    〈 Distributivity of ⋁ over ≡ 〉
  p ⋁ ¬p ≡ p ⋁ p
=    〈 Excluded middle; Idempotency of ⋁ 〉
  true ≡ p
=    〈 Identity of ≡ 〉
  p  ╱╱

